    <item>
      <title>英国监管机构要求在线服务机构“立即行动”以制止骚乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-regulator-tells-online-services-to-act-now-to-stop-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管英国电信监管机构 Ofcom 出台的更严格监管网络内容的新规定尚未生效，但英国电信监管机构仍敦促网络服务提供商采取行动，阻止客户使用其平台煽动暴力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/uk-regulator-tells-online-services-to-act-now-to-stop-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行家从佛罗里达州的增长热潮中收获了 150 亿美元的市政债券交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bankers-reap-15-billion-of-muni-deals-from-florida-growth-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[佛罗里达州向华尔街南部的转变正推动新移民的激增，对全州的基础设施造成冲击，并迫使各市政府以十多年来最快的速度借贷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/bankers-reap-15-billion-of-muni-deals-from-florida-growth-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:50:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
